Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast! My school for the next 4 years.

Name: UCSB Apartment
Description: This has been my home since Jan. 4th of 2021. I moved to Santa Barbara during winter break to focus my education on campus.

Name: My Home of 12 Years
Description: I have lived in this house since I was 7 years old. I grew up here; this is where my family is; so close to my friends and extended family throughout my life.

Name: Boyfriend's Hometown
Description: Fellows, CA is where my boyfriend is living; I now have several life long friends, a new puppy, and another family in this town.

Name: Barstow
Description: The Cazares (my family), the Hastings, and family friends went to the desert to go dirt bike riding and camping. We went once every month during Fall and Winter; these times were our prime time. However, we stopped going once our grandfather passed away; we didn't want to go without him. It was his favorite thing to do.

Name: Corona Del Mar
Description: This beach was my home away from home Summer 2019. I was there every single day with or without friends to go with me. This beach has stairs that I would workout on, a large sand hill to climb over to get to the private beach, and the drive there was, heaven.
